ail, state and local government, education, legal services, real estate, technology, insurance, construction and hospitality, and others. The company sells its products to enterprise customers, and small and medium-sized businesses through resellers and distributors, partners, and global service providers. RingCentral, Inc. was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Belmont, California.", "fullTimeEmployees": 7378, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Vladimir G. Shmunis", "age": 64, "title": "Co-Founder, CEO & Executive Chairman", "yearBorn": 1961, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 1076959, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Kira  Makagon", "age": 62, "title": "President & COO", "yearBorn": 1963, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 1043094, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Vaibhav  Agarwal", "age": 48, "title": "Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1977, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 1037434, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. John H. Marlow J.D.", "age": 56, "title": "Chief Administrative Officer, SVP of Corporate Development, General Counsel & Secretary", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 964711, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Vlad  Vendrow", "title": "Co-Founder & CTO", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Tarun  Arora", "age": 46, "title": "Chief Accounting Officer", "yearBorn": 1979, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Steven  Horwitz", "title": "Vice President of Investor Relations", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Carson  Hostetter", "title": "Executive VP and GM of CX & AI", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Homayoun  Razavi", "title": "Executive VP & G